I was going to ask you to, if I could beg your indulgence, could I possibly send my four books and have them autographed?

15:20.940 --> 15:21.380
Oh, God.

15:21.380 --> 15:26.560
And I will put in the return postage and the label and all that, and I would be,

15:27.580 --> 15:28.480
Oh, well thank you.

15:28.540 --> 15:29.560
